---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Community - Connect with Fellow English Learners in London"
  description="Join buddy programs, practice groups, and community events designed to help international students connect, learn, and thrive together in London."
>
  <Header />

  <section
    class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center relative overflow-hidden pt-16 font-sans"
  >
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
      <img
        src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/1595391/pexels-photo-1595391.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1920&h=1080&fit=crop"
        alt="International students connecting"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-30"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-cream/60 to-cream/90">
      </div>
    </div>

    <div
      class="relative z-10 text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"
    >
      <h1
        class="font-sans font-bold text-5xl md:text-7xl text-charcoal leading-tight mb-6"
      >
        Find Your Tribe
      </h1>
      <p
        class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-charcoal/80 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed"
      >
        Connect with like-minded international students through our buddy
        programs, practice groups, and community events designed to turn
        strangers into lifelong friends.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 bg-white font-sans">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="font-script text-earth text-lg mb-4">How we connect</h2>
        <h3 class="font-sans font-bold text-4xl md:text-5xl text-charcoal">
          Community Programs
        </h3>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-20">
        <div>
          <img
            src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/1438072/pexels-photo-1438072.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800&h=600&fit=crop"
            alt="Buddy program meeting"
            class="w-full rounded-2xl shadow-lg"
          />
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-sans font-bold text-3xl text-charcoal mb-6">
            Buddy Program
          </h3>
          <p class="text-lg text-charcoal/70 mb-6">
            Get paired with a local London student or someone who's been here
            longer. Your buddy will help you navigate the city, practice English
            in real situations, and become your first friend in London. It's
            like having a local best friend from day one.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-earth mr-3 mt-1">✓</span>
              <span>One-on-one matching based on interests and goals</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-earth mr-3 mt-1">✓</span>
              <span>Weekly meetups for conversation practice</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-earth mr-3 mt-1">✓</span>
              <span>London exploration and cultural exchange</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="bg-earth text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full hover:bg-charcoal transition-all duration-300 font-medium"
          >
            Join Buddy Program
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-20">
        <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
          <h3 class="font-sans font-bold text-3xl text-charcoal mb-6">
            Practice Groups
          </h3>
          <p class="text-lg text-charcoal/70 mb-6">
            Small, friendly groups that meet regularly to practice English in a
            relaxed, supportive environment. Whether you want to work on
            conversation, pronunciation, or just build confidence, there's a
            group perfect for you.
          </p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6">
            <div class="bg-cream p-4 rounded-xl">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-charcoal mb-2">
                Conversation Circles
              </h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/70">
                Weekly relaxed chats over coffee
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-cream p-4 rounded-xl">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-charcoal mb-2">
                Pronunciation Labs
              </h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/70">
                Practice tricky sounds together
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-cream p-4 rounded-xl">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-charcoal mb-2">Business English</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/70">
                Professional communication skills
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-cream p-4 rounded-xl">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-charcoal mb-2">IELTS Support</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/70">
                Exam preparation with peers
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <a
            href="/events"
            class="bg-earth text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full hover:bg-charcoal transition-all duration-300 font-medium"
          >
            Find Practice Groups
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
          <img
            src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/1595391/pexels-photo-1595391.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800&h=600&fit=crop"
            alt="Practice group session"
            class="w-full rounded-2xl shadow-lg"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 bg-beige font-sans">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="font-script text-earth text-lg mb-4">What's happening</h2>
        <h3 class="font-sans font-bold text-4xl md:text-5xl text-charcoal">
          Upcoming Community Events
        </h3>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div
          class="bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300"
        >
          <img
            src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/2422588/pexels-photo-2422588.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=400&h=250&fit=crop"
            alt="London walk event"
            class="w-full h-48 object-cover"
          />
          <div class="p-6">
            <div class="text-earth font-semibold text-sm mb-2">
              This Saturday, 2:00 PM
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-sans font-bold text-xl text-charcoal mb-3">
              Hidden London Walking Tour
            </h4>
            <p class="text-charcoal/70 mb-4">
              Discover secret spots in Central London while practicing English
              with fellow students. Free for community members!
            </p>
            <a href="/events" class="text-earth font-medium hover:underline"
              >Join this event →</a
            >
          </div>
        </div>

        <div
          class="bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300"
        >
          <img
            src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/3184360/pexels-photo-3184360.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=400&h=250&fit=crop"
            alt="Cooking class"
            class="w-full h-48 object-cover"
          />
          <div class="p-6">
            <div class="text-earth font-semibold text-sm mb-2">
              Tuesday, 6:30 PM
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-sans font-bold text-xl text-charcoal mb-3">
              International Cooking Night
            </h4>
            <p class="text-charcoal/70 mb-4">
              Share recipes from your home country while learning food
              vocabulary and making new friends. Bring an appetite!
            </p>
            <a href="/events" class="text-earth font-medium hover:underline"
              >Join this event →</a
            >
          </div>
        </div>

        <div
          class="bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300"
        >
          <img
            src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/1181467/pexels-photo-1181467.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=400&h=250&fit=crop"
            alt="Game night"
            class="w-full h-48 object-cover"
          />
          <div class="p-6">
            <div class="text-earth font-semibold text-sm mb-2">
              Friday, 7:00 PM
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-sans font-bold text-xl text-charcoal mb-3">
              Game Night & Karaoke
            </h4>
            <p class="text-charcoal/70 mb-4">
              Fun evening of board games and karaoke to practice English in the
              most relaxed way possible. Beginners welcome!
            </p>
            <a href="/events" class="text-earth font-medium hover:underline"
              >Join this event →</a
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center mt-12">
        <a
          href="/events"
          class="bg-earth text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full text-lg font-medium hover:bg-charcoal transition-all duration-300"
        >
          View All Events
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 bg-white font-sans">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-script text-earth text-lg mb-4">
        What our community says
      </h2>
      <h3 class="font-sans font-bold text-4xl md:text-5xl text-charcoal mb-12">
        Real connections, real impact
      </h3>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-cream rounded-2xl p-8">
          <p class="text-lg text-charcoal/80 mb-6 italic">
            "I joined the buddy program feeling nervous and shy. Three months
            later, I have a best friend, improved English, and I actually look
            forward to social events. This community changed my London
            experience completely."
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <img
              src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/1181690/pexels-photo-1181690.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=100&h=100&fit=crop"
              alt="Sofia from Spain"
              class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full mr-4"
            />
            <div class="text-left">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-charcoal">Sofia Martinez</h4>
              <p class="text-charcoal/60 text-sm">From Spain, here 8 months</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-cream rounded-2xl p-8">
          <p class="text-lg text-charcoal/80 mb-6 italic">
            "The practice groups are amazing! It's not like school - we actually
            laugh, share stories, and help each other. My confidence in speaking
            English has grown so much since I started attending."
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <img
              src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/1040880/pexels-photo-1040880.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=100&h=100&fit=crop"
              alt="Chen from China"
              class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full mr-4"
            />
            <div class="text-left">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-charcoal">Chen Wei</h4>
              <p class="text-charcoal/60 text-sm">From China, here 6 months</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
